0.1 Core Backend
================
OK	Logging
OK	VO Serialization
OK	Persistence NoSQL (Objectify)
OK	IoD (Spring core)
OK	Spring AOP (Interception) 
OK	Service Bean (EJB like) 
	Transactions (Appengine/Objectify) (commit/rollback)
	Exceptions
	i18n
	Bean Validation
	Many Spring Application Context xml confs
	

0.2 Core View
============
	Spring MVC (see http://www.mkyong.com/spring3/spring-3-mvc-hello-world-example/)
	JSON (http://www.mkyong.com/spring-mvc/spring-3-mvc-and-json-example/)
	REST (see http://www.mkyong.com/spring-mvc/spring-3-rest-hello-world-example/)
	Taglib Xtension
	JavaScript Lib (JQuery)
	Mobile (JQuery)

0.3 Security
============
	OAuth 2.0 with Google
	OAuth 2.0 with facebook
	
	
	

